Group(pl):	Narzêdzia/Archiwizacja
Source:		ftp://alpha.gnu.org/gnu/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
Patch0:		gzip-basename.patch
Patch1:		gzip-gzexe.patch
Patch2:		gzip-mktemp.patch
Patch3:		gzip-info.patch
